  "detailed_description": "<br><br>Polyoshapes is an captivating puzzle game consisting of 60 levels in which players strategically place different geometric shapes on a grid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825510/extras/40b4c1dcfca8e6e0df9abeb4f8b34264.poster.avif?t=1765508569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825510/extras/40b4c1dcfca8e6e0df9abeb4f8b34264.webm?t=1765508569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825510/extras/40b4c1dcfca8e6e0df9abeb4f8b34264.mp4?t=1765508569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The goal is to fill the grid by arranging the shapes in a way that maximizes space utilization and minimizes gaps. With an increasing level of complexity, players must use their spatial reasoning and problem-solving skills to complete each puzzle.",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br>Polyoshapes is an captivating puzzle game consisting of 60 levels in which players strategically place different geometric shapes on a grid.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825510/extras/40b4c1dcfca8e6e0df9abeb4f8b34264.poster.avif?t=1765508569\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825510/extras/40b4c1dcfca8e6e0df9abeb4f8b34264.webm?t=1765508569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2825510/extras/40b4c1dcfca8e6e0df9abeb4f8b34264.mp4?t=1765508569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The goal is to fill the grid by arranging the shapes in a way that maximizes space utilization and minimizes gaps. With an increasing level of complexity, players must use their spatial reasoning and problem-solving skills to complete each puzzle.",
